<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.9.2">
<l>uḷaṉāka vēyeṇṇit taṉṉaiyoṉ ṟākattaṉ celvattai</l>
<l>vaḷaṉā matikkumim māṉiṭat taikkavi pāṭiyeṉ</l>
<l>kuḷaṉār kaḻaṉicūḻ kaṇṇaṉ kuṟuṅkuṭi meymmaiyē</l>
<l>yuḷaṉāya ventaiyai yentaipem māṉai yoḻiyavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What of singing a poem on this humaniry who thinks its wealth</l>
<l>to be riches, for it to be one, while thinking that he is</l>
<l>our father, except the great lord our father, that he is</l>
<l>in truth Kṛṣṇa in Kuṟuṅkuṭi sourrounded by paddy fields full of tanks.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
